results.name: Denominators of row sums in triangle described in A093412.
mathematica: Do[s = i = n; j = 1; x = i; y = j; While[x/y != 1, i--; j++; x += i; y += j; s += x/y]; Print[Denominator[s]], {n, 1, 30}] (* _Ryan Propper_, Aug 16 2005 *)
